<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.6.1">
<l>toṇṭī ruyyum vakaikaṇṭēṉ tuḷaṅkā varakkar tuḷaṅkamuṉ</l>
<l>tiṇṭōḷ nimirac cilaivaḷaiyac ciṟitē muṉinta tirumārpaṉ</l>
<l>vaṇṭār kūntal malarmaṅkai vaṭikkaṇ maṭantai mānōkkam</l>
<l>kaṇṭāṉ kaṇṭu koṇṭukanta kaṇṇa puramnām toḻutumē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Devotees, I saw the way which will save [us]! We will worship in Kaṇṇapuram</l>
<l rend="indent">where rejoiced, having seen [that place] for himself,</l>
<l>The one with Tiru at his chest who quickly angered so he bent the bow</l>
<l>As he stretched his strong arm long ago so that the fearless demons feared,</l>
<l>The one who saw the deer-like glances of the lady of the blossom</l>
<l rend="indent">with bee-filled tresses [and] of the long-eyed lady.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
